# üìö 1000 Books Web Scraping Project

This project scrapes **1000 books** from the practice website:  
**http://books.toscrape.com**

### What data was collected?
- Book Title
- Price (in ¬£)
- Star Rating (One ‚òÖ to Five ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ)
- Availability (In stock or not)
- Book Cover Image URL

### Tools / Libraries used
- requests
- BeautifulSoup (bs4)
- pandas

### Files in this repository
| File name                        | Description                              |
|----------------------------------|------------------------------------------|
| `book_to_scraped.ipynb`          | Jupyter notebook with full scraping code |
| `1000_books_50page_info.xls`     | Final scraped data (Excel file)          |
| `1000_books_50page_info.csv`     | Final scraped data (CSV file)            |

### Website used for practice
‚Üí http://books.toscrape.com/catalogue/page-1.html  
(This is a free dummy bookstore made only for learning web scraping)

### Important Note
This project is made **only for learning and practice**.  
